# 從頭再嚟
(pos: 成語/動詞短語)
<explanation>
yue: 由開始嘅地方重新開始做某件事，通常係因為之前失敗咗或者想做得更好（量詞：次）
eng: to start all over again; to begin from scratch
<eg>
yue: 個計劃失敗咗，我哋唯有從頭再嚟。 (gong3 gei3 faai3 baat1 zo2, ngo5 dei6 wai4 jau5 cung4 tau4 zoi3 lei4.)
eng: The plan failed, so we have to start all over again.

yue: 你唔好咁心急，就算做錯咗都可以從頭再嚟。 (nei5 m4 hou2 gam3 sam1 sap3, zau6 syun6 zou3 co3 zo2 dou1 ho2 yi1 cung4 tau4 zoi3 lei4.)
eng: Don't be so impatient; even if you make a mistake, you can start over. [end of text]


